(Soulstice, how do Deemos and everyone know about Vulois, know about 
his mission of peace, and know where his base is?)

Vulois, through his anger, got the message.

"JUST SETTLE DOWN! I'll be down to see you."

Vulois left his room and stormed down into the tunnels to go get Atma 
Pseudo and Technosis, and didn't tell anyone where he was going.
